Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.32,0:00:45.38,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,うまいこと泳ぐな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.58,0:01:11.74,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,さてと
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.85,0:01:27.81,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,お　悪いな
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.09,0:01:29.89,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,煙たかったか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.63,0:01:37.88,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やけに冷たいな　水に入ってたにしろ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.38,0:01:41.19,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,涌太
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.44,0:01:48.43,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,涌太 どうしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:52.16,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの　一体何が…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:54.42,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いや　申し訳ない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.37,0:01:56.99,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,タバコの煙吸っちまったみたいで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.91,0:02:00.69,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,母ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.00,0:02:07.95,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今日もたくさん取れたわね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:11.90,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,さあ　もう帰るわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.77,0:02:15.34,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.25,0:02:16.84,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何か
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.99,0:02:20.47,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その子　泳ぎは達者だが　
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:22.67,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,走るのは少々不得手では
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.22,0:02:26.45,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,だったら何なの
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.56,0:02:31.19,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,異様に　喉の渇きを訴えたりは？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:39.08,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何が 言いたいんですか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:50.50,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,幾つか　われわれ蟲師の記録と符合する点がありましてね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.93,0:02:55.57,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,低い体温　言葉の遅れ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:03:00.10,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,稀に　水掻きのあるものも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:04.19,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それがなんだってんです？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:06.55,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,妙な言いがかりは…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:07.97,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それらの原因が蟲なら
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:10.22,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,影響を薄める薬があります
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:14.92,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やはり　他の子と様子が違うのは
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.16,0:03:17.82,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いろいろと不安なんじゃないですか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:31.85,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,水を掻いてんのか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:35.53,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,夢の中でも泳いでんのかね
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:02.37,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの子の中には　雨蠱という蟲がいます
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:09.52,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,個体としては　肉眼では捉えられないほど小さなもの
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:15.34,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それが雨に紛れ川へ流れ込むと
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.75,0:04:20.28,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,群れて碧い巨大魚のような姿で川を下り
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:24.99,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やがて海に出て　子を成す
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.20,0:04:29.86,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それがまた水蒸気に紛れ　
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.64,0:04:32.36,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,雨となり　山河に降り注ぐ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:37.98,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうして生きているものに過ぎないが
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.52,0:04:44.32,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,川を下るときに　群れの一部が淵などに取り残されると
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:50.06,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,魚に食われないように 山椒魚などの体内に寄生する
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.74,0:04:54.37,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,が　ごく稀に
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.39,0:04:58.10,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,溺れて仮死状態となった人に寄生することもある
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:03.01,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうなると　蘇生はするが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:07.49,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,息子さんのような影響が残り　完全に抜くことはできない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.53,0:05:14.91,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,大水が起こると　濁流に乗じて海へ出ようと
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.80,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,自ら抜け出ることもあるが
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:19.15,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,いつ起こるとも分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.32,0:05:25.53,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まずは暫く　この薬で様子を見てください
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.18,0:06:06.94,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,涌太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.98,0:06:15.72,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,涌太
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:20.91,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,夜は来ちゃだめだって言ってるでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.50,0:06:25.58,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,また　水の夢を見たのね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:51.97,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,母ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.67,0:06:56.19,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,すごいの取れたわね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:04.60,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ほら
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.54,0:07:11.19,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:12.90,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,入れてやんねぇぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.83,0:07:17.25,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あいつ　体が魚みてぇに冷てぇんだってさ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:18.80,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,人の子じゃねぇんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.43,0:07:20.24,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,気味悪い
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:28.24,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:31.90,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,うわ　でっけぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.86,0:07:35.64,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,向こう　たくさんいる
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.95,0:07:39.05,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,一緒遊ぼう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.92,0:07:44.42,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そっち
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:48.29,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,下手くそ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:53.22,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれ　お前　そんな体冷たくねぇな
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.31,0:07:56.04,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,本当だ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.82,0:07:58.38,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,誰が冷てぇとか言ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:07:59.52,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,さあ　
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:06.42,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ね　母ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:08.06,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.69,0:08:10.42,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,川はどこから来る？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:13.84,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,山奥の谷から流れてくるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.36,0:08:17.31,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,谷の水　どこから来る？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.97,0:08:20.18,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,空の雲から降ってくるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:23.17,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　空の雲は？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.57,0:08:27.83,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,えっと　あっそう　海から生まれるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.31,0:08:30.03,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.99,0:08:33.00,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この川が行き着くところよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:35.98,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,たくさん水があるところ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:39.50,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,たくさん？どれぐらい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:43.66,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,母さんもまだ見たことないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:46.46,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,見渡す限り水なんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:48.46,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,へえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.74,0:08:54.15,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　海も川も雨も雲も全部一緒？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.66,0:08:59.94,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうよ　形は違うけど　みんな同じなの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.16,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:10.36,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.38,0:09:15.52,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何でもないわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.70,0:09:29.48,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,元気そうだな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:33.60,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あ　煙のおじさん
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:35.27,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おじさん…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:38.24,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう　煙はいやじゃねぇのか
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:40.84,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,うん　そんなに
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.14,0:09:50.41,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,薬が効いたみたいだな
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:52.08,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,はい　
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.14,0:09:55.14,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,体温もずいぶん上がりましたし
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.15,0:09:59.00,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,以前は日に一升も水を欲しがりましたが
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:01.58,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,今は七合ほどに減ってきてます
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:03.67,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そりゃよかった
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:05.93,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ありがとうございます
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:09.70,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの薬　またいただけますか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:14.76,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,言っておくが　恐らくこれ以上の効果は望めない
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:18.20,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,蟲が抜けたわけではないのでね
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.40,0:10:23.09,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,本来　人に寄生するものではないから
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:25.44,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,人とはそう深く結びつかないが
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:29.66,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,山椒魚などは　寄生されて数年たつと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.93,0:10:31.46,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,同化して水に消えてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:36.08,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そういう　厄介なものなんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.73,0:10:38.48,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:41.67,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でもあの子は大丈夫なんでしょ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:47.22,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,恐らく　薬で影響を抑えながら現状を保てるはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.11,0:10:52.21,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,それでよければ　また頃合を見て薬を持ってくる
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:55.88,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ま　薬代は安くしとくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.10,0:11:02.01,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうね　それで充分
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.54,0:11:06.18,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おじさん
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:07.11,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おじさんじゃねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.79,0:11:10.00,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,次　いつ来る？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.32,0:11:13.53,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,んん　秋口だ　
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:17.43,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃあな　もう溺れんなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:20.92,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おれ　溺れたことないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:23.95,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,嘘付け　忘れてんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.67,0:11:26.68,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おい　涌太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.02,0:11:30.10,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　またね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:53.08,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,涌太　
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:55.31,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,中へ入ってなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:13.03,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:17.21,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,喉が乾いたの　川は駄目よ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:19.78,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,行かなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.62,0:12:24.13,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何言って　待ちなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.33,0:12:27.27,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,涌太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.79,0:12:39.33,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,涌太　どこ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.86,0:12:43.91,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ギンコさん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:46.22,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ここらが長雨だと聞いてな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:49.69,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,このままだと　鉄砲水が来る
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.77,0:12:55.22,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,危険も伴うが　上手くいきゃ雨蠱を抜けるかもしれん
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.28,0:12:58.28,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,やるなら手を貸す
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:08.85,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ごめんね　我慢してね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:12.92,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でも　こうすればあんたも　
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.60,0:13:15.71,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,きっと他の子たちと同じになれる
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:20.63,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,村の皆に認めてもらえる子に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:39.14,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じっとして　危ないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.01,0:13:42.00,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,行かなきゃ　
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.32,0:13:46.29,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう行かなきゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.75,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,何言ってるの　
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:50.36,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,止めなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:56.04,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,絶対に　絶対にどこへもやらないから
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.90,0:15:14.22,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,涌太　起きて　朝よ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.58,0:15:22.85,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,涌太　返事して
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:26.88,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,母ちゃん
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:29.58,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,良かった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.73,0:15:33.97,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,母ちゃん　どうしたの
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:40.18,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,雨怖かったね　もう怖くないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:45.09,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ええ　そうね
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:49.90,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,雨蠱は抜けた…のか
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:56.38,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねえ　母ちゃん　喉乾いた
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.12,0:15:58.70,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そう　
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.38,0:16:02.89,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,川の水は泥が混ざっちゃったから
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.47,0:16:05.11,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,山のほうの井戸まで行こうか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.14,0:16:20.69,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,未だ喉の渇きを訴える 抜き切っていないのか
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.51,0:16:29.30,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうしたんです
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.35,0:16:32.71,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,おかしい　体がひどく熱い
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:35.19,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,とにかく水を
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.59,0:16:38.46,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,涌太
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:50.63,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,涌太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.76,0:17:05.56,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,涌…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.08,0:17:09.77,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どこ　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:12.36,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どこへ消えたの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.86,0:17:17.66,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どこなの
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.18,0:17:28.33,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,ねえ　母ちゃん　
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.52,0:17:31.60,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,川　どこから来る？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.46,0:17:37.21,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,山の奥の谷から流れて来るのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.31,0:17:41.78,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,谷の水　どこから来る？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:45.15,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,空の雲から降ってくるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:49.84,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　空の雲は？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.42,0:17:52.85,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,海から生まれるのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.64,0:17:55.37,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,海？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:18:01.16,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,この川の行き着く所よ　たくさん水のある所
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:11.68,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうして　あの子は
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:21.84,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの子は　自分は溺れたことはないと言っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.89,0:18:26.91,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,川で溺れたのは
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:29.15,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あんたか
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.47,0:18:35.05,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:44.48,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あれは　あの子の生まれる十月ほど前のことです
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:49.15,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,なんだか今日は流れが速いな
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:52.15,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,山で雨が降ったのかしら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.13,0:19:03.73,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,気が付くと　私は岸にいました
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:06.52,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,けれど　夫は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.34,0:19:10.11,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,深みの底で見つかりました　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:17.25,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その後　私は夫の子を身ごもっていることに気づきました
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.02,0:19:25.41,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,腹の中で無事でいてくれたことに 心底感謝しました
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:30.70,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう一息だよ　頑張って　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.66,0:19:32.30,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:41.04,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,タキさん　気の毒だけど　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:49.80,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,冷たい赤児でした
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.99,0:19:52.67,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,けれど　
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:59.57,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,その子は確かに生きていました
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.09,0:20:04.58,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,皆　恐ろしいと言ったけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.63,0:20:07.00,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,私は嬉しかった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.72,0:20:13.91,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,普通でないなりに　これまで生きてくれてたんです
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.87,0:20:19.78,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうして　今になって…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.27,0:20:26.36,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,胎児は腹の中で水に浸されていて　
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.56,0:20:31.56,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,人よりも蛙や山椒魚　水の生き物に近いという
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:37.38,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの子はその段階で雨蠱に寄生された
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:42.88,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そして　そのまま体内で成長していくうちに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.64,0:20:47.78,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,分類できないほど深く深く一体化してしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.37,0:20:54.22,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,私が　私がそんなものに憑かれたせいで
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:59.48,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あの子が腹の中で無事だったのは
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:03.63,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,まず　あんたが雨蠱に寄生されて蘇生したからだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:09.08,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,でなけりゃ　二人とも生きてはいなかったろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.21,0:21:13.08,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,あいつは生きた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.65,0:21:17.96,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,確かにここに　
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.80,0:21:20.53,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,生きていた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.45,0:21:30.50,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,じゃあ　海も川も雨も雲も　全部一緒？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.33,0:21:38.60,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうよ　形は違っても　皆同じなの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.79,0:21:48.33,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,涌太　あんた今どこにいる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.34,0:21:57.30,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,川かしら　海かしら　雨かしら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.96,0:22:03.83,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,どうしたの　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:07.83,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,もう怖くないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.16,0:22:27.18,TXT JP G-OTF Kyoukasho ICA Pro M,,0,0,0,,そうだね　あんたはどこにでもいるんだものね
